        },
        "subject": "LU-11512 ldiskfs: DL-SNAP Directory Level Snapshot",
        "message": "LU-11512 ldiskfs: DL-SNAP Directory Level Snapshot\n\nDL-SNAP is a feature designed for directory level file backups.\n\nIt is implemented on top of lustre ldiskfs without\nmodification of ext4 disk format,\nthough we set a special original flag to FEATURE of the superblock\nin order to check whether DL-SNAP is enabled.\n\nSigned-off-by: Takamura Tatsushi <takamr.tatsushi@jp.fujitsu.com>\nChange-Id: I235d448379d9dd69b262127ded76ce3bd7df596d\n"
      },
